nl.yrck.datastructures

Class OpenAddressingDatastructure

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.yrck.datastructures.OpenAddressingDatastructure
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Datastructure

    public class OpenAddressingDatastructure
extends java.lang.Object
implements Datastructure
    Implementation of Open Addressing hashtable

    An Open Addressing works by probing the next open hash when a hash collision occurs. This class uses Linear probing for this.

    Author:
    Yorick de Boer
